T*
(Applied remediations for the lockbox security audit findings:) Tj
T*
(- plaintext backup leakage:) Tj
T*
(- encrypted migration no longer emits new plaintext pre_write backup,) Tj
T*
(- encrypted save path purges existing plaintext-secret backups under Keys/backups/.) Tj
T*
(- plaintext mnemonic sidecar leakage:) Tj
T*
(- enabling encrypted-at-rest lockbox now removes plaintext files in Keys/mnemonic_recovery/....) Tj
T*
(- unlock session persistence:) Tj
T*
(- API refresh now uses key-file fingerprint caching so unchanged files do not reset unlock) Tj
T*
(state.) Tj
T*
(- unlock brute-force controls:) Tj
T*
(- per-client backoff + lockout on repeated /wallet/unlock failures.) Tj
T*
(- KDF parameter bounds:) Tj
T*
(- Argon2id metadata is now range-validated to prevent resource-exhaustion unlock payloads.) Tj
T*
(- in-memory unlock secret:) Tj
T*
(- migrated to mutable bytes with zeroization on lock/expiry.) Tj
T*
(- Kyber wrapper trust boundary:) Tj
T*
(- external lib path loading now opt-in \(ATHO_KYBER_ALLOW_EXTERNAL_LIB=1\); default is trusted) Tj
T*
(vendored path only.) Tj
T*
(- Kyber lockbox requirement:) Tj
T*
(- wallet lockbox now requires Kyber DEK wrapping for encrypted-at-rest payloads.) Tj
T*
(- Kyber opt-out requests are rejected.) Tj
T*
(- Advanced unlock mode:) Tj
T*
(- wallet now supports unlock_mode=advanced, which requires Kyber unlock .txt bundle import plus) Tj
T*
(password at unlock.) Tj
T*
(- bundle schema is strict \(athokey-kyber-unlock-v1\) with integrity hash + binding checks;) Tj
T*
(tampered files are rejected.) Tj
T*
(- unlock status metadata:) Tj
T*
(- absolute key-file path hidden by default.) Tj
T*
